queries.name: InnerJoinQuery
queries.query: SELECT * FROM customer INNER JOIN orders ON customer.Cust_ID=orders.Customer_ID ORDER BY customer.Cust_ID

queries.name: LeftOuterJoinQuery
queries.query: SELECT * FROM customer LEFT OUTER JOIN orders ON customer.Cust_ID = orders.Customer_ID ORDER BY customer.Cust_ID

queries.name: RightOuterJoinquery
queries.query: SELECT * FROM customer right OUTER JOIN orders ON customer.Cust_ID=orders.Customer_ID ORDER BY customer.Cust_ID

queries.name: FullOuterJoinQuery
queries.query:
SELECT * FROM customer LEFT OUTER JOIN orders ON customer.Cust_ID=orders.Customer_ID 
Union all 
SELECT * FROM customer right OUTER JOIN orders ON customer.Cust_ID=orders.Customer_ID
